Full Day Kindergarten Information



The Lockport School District 91 Board Of Education is pleased to announce their approval of full day kindergarten at Milne Grove School for the 20-21 school year! In order to project staffing, we are requesting prospective kindergarten students register by April 1, 2020. Beginning on February 24th, online registration will be open through our Infinite Campus portal; simply visit our website on the 24th or after to access information and forms. Please contact Mrs. Koziol at jkoziol@d91.net with your full day kindergarten questions or to join our kindergarten email list.
















